| Shared-infra consumed | {{SHARED_INFRA_MODULES}} |
| Depends on (other modules) | {{MODULE_DEPS}} |

## 3. Data model

Design rigorously (see the data-schema note above). Document the entities, keys, and the
**constraints that enforce invariants in the database**, not just in app code.

| Entity | Key fields | Notable constraints (FK / CHECK / unique / exclusion / effective-dating) |
|--------|-----------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| `{{ENTITY_1}}` | {{KEYS_1}} | {{CONSTRAINTS_1}} |
| `{{ENTITY_2}}` | {{KEYS_2}} | {{CONSTRAINTS_2}} |

- **Append-only audit:** which fields are audited (one row per changed field); reference the shared
  audit primitive — do not hand-log.
- **Effective-dating / temporal:** which rows are effective-dated and how non-overlap is enforced.

